Package soot.toolkits.graph

Class MemoryEfficientGraph<N>

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toolkits.graph.HashMutableDirectedGraph<N>
      • soot.toolkits.graph.MemoryEfficientGraph<N>
  • Type Parameters:
    N -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<N>, DirectedGraph<N>, MutableDirectedGraph<N>
    public class MemoryEfficientGraph<N>
extends HashMutableDirectedGraph<N>
    A memory efficient version of HashMutableDirectedGraph, in the sense that throw-away objects passed as arguments will not be kept in the process of adding edges.
